Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.19,0:22:20.19,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭粗黑_GBK\fs30\bord0\c&H000000&\fad(504,0)\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1\pos(305,575)}距退学所差「雷电」: 7颗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.19,0:22:20.19,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭粗黑_GBK\fs30\bord0\c&H000000&\fad(504,0)\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1\pos(305,640)}学习能力+5
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.27,0:22:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,什么  任务失败了?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,骗我的吧  我明明已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,开除?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我传说的帷幕啊
